      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark test cases at MRL 2 level.",
      "rationale": "The ANSYS Fluent solver has been verified against standard CFD benchmark cases including lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step flows. Code verification documentation is available in the solver validation manual."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
