      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be reported and discretization error must be below 5% for primary QoI at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was performed on the centrifugal pump geometry. GCI for the normalized index of hemolysis was 3.2%, satisfying the MRL 2 threshold. Medium mesh (4.2M elements) selected for production runs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
