      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must be documented with sufficient fidelity to enable reproduction of boundary conditions in the CFD model.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic pump experimental conditions are fully documented including inlet flow rates (2–6 L/min), rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM), fluid temperature (37°C), and hematocrit (35%). All boundary conditions are reproducible from published data."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
