      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be conducted at conditions representative of the CPB COU operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted using the FDA generic centrifugal pump at CPB-representative flow rates and speeds. The validation domain encompasses the full operating envelope specified in the COU, supporting extrapolation confidence."
    },
