    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Uncertainty quantification across primary model inputs confirms that the 95th-percentile hemolysis index remains within the acceptance criterion (RH < 1). The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission.",
